OL,3,CDoctors in Isle of Man vote in favour
OL,4,Cof industrial action for very first
OL,5,Ctime
OL,7,FDoctors in the Isle of Man have voted
OL,8,Fin favour of industrial action for the
OL,9,Fvery first time, in an ongoing dispute
OL,10,Fover pay.
OL,12,FA total of 121 of the 127 doctors
OL,13,Fvoted yes in the ballot, calling on
OL,14,FManx Care for a 12.6% uplift in pay.
OL,16,FThe British Medical Association (BMA)
OL,17,Fsay doctors have experienced 'real
OL,18,Fterms pay cuts' since 2008, with some
OL,19,Fas much as 19%.
