OL,5,Ctime
OL,7,FSince 2008, inflation on the island
OL,8,Fhas increased by 56.3% while the
OL,9,Fmaximum consultant's salary increased
OL,10,Fby just 27.3% over the same period.
OL,12,FIn October this year, the BMA found
OL,13,Fonly 15% of those who took part would
OL,14,Frecommend the Island's main healthcare
OL,15,Fprovider Manx Care, as a good place to
OL,16,Fwork.
OL,18,FOf those who responded, only 9% felt
OL,19,Fthey were being heard , while 81%
OL,20,Fdisagreed with the statement 'Manx
OL,21,FCare has a positive culture'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
