OL,7,FThe healthcare service, which launched
OL,8,Fin 2021, says it is working with
OL,9,Fdoctors to resolve their differences.
OL,11,FDespite a series of meetings between
OL,12,FBMA representatives and Manx Care, a
OL,13,Fdeal has not yet been reached.
OL,15,FChair of the Isle of Man Medical
OL,16,FSociety, Dr Prakash Thiagarajan, said:
OL,17,F"We've now got a clear mandate from
OL,18,Four members that Manx Care cannot
OL,19,Fignore.
