OL,7,F"I hope we can still avoid strike
OL,8,Faction, and that Manx Care will now
OL,9,Fcome to us in good faith to find a
OL,10,Fsolution that values the work we do.
OL,11,FDoctors want to give patients the best
OL,12,Fpossible care and that's achieved by
OL,13,Fimproving the working lives of doctors
OL,14,Fand the first step towards such
OL,15,Fimprovement is reduction of the years
OL,16,Fof pay erosion we have suffered."
