OL,7,FProfessor Phil Banfield, Chair of
OL,8,Fcouncil at the BMA, said: "Doctors on
OL,9,Fthe Isle of Man are overworked,
OL,10,Funderpaid and overlooked. These
OL,11,Fdoctors deserve to be treated with
OL,12,Ffairness and respect. Their resident,
OL,13,Fconsultant and SAS colleagues across
OL,14,Fthe UK have fought for, and won, pay
OL,15,Fuplifts as their first step on a
OL,16,Fjourney to restoring the lost value of
OL,17,Ftheir pay.
