OL,7,F"Doctors on the Isle of Man deserve
OL,8,Fthe same. The BMA has organised and
OL,9,Fsupported this ballot at the request
OL,10,Fof its members, and we will continue
OL,11,Fto support Manx doctors in fighting
OL,12,Ffor appropriate recognition of their
OL,13,Fskills and expertise they bring to the
OL,14,FIsland's patients."
