OL,7,FResponding the results of the survey,
OL,8,FManx Care said: "We recognise the
OL,9,Finvaluable contribution of our
OL,10,Fdoctors, and believe they deserve a
OL,11,Ffair pay rise. However, we must manage
OL,12,Four finances and stay within our
OL,13,Fbudget.
