OL,7,F"For the next year Government has been
OL,8,Fclear that there will be no additional
OL,9,Ffunding beyond what has already been
OL,10,Fallocated. Spending more than what has
OL,11,Fbeen allocated for pay rises would
OL,12,Fmean reallocating funding from other
OL,13,Fservices, potentially leading to cuts
OL,14,For service reductions.
OL,16,F"Manx Care has negotiated within their
OL,17,Fbudget and offered several solutions.
