OL,5,Ctime
OL,7,F"We are pleased that Manx Care and the
OL,8,FBMA continue to move forward with
OL,9,Ftheir negotiations, and are committed
OL,10,Fto further discussions early in the
OL,11,FNew Year.
OL,13,F"We respect the right of our workforce
OL,14,Fto take action, and the DHSC will work
OL,15,Fclosely with Manx Care to support them
OL,16,Fto reduce harm and the impact to the
OL,17,Fpublic should the strikes go ahead."
